text: Hello! Not all of our members are guys. In an effort to be more conscious of the language we use to address each other, why not try “Hey, folks,” or “Hey everyone” instead?

Hello everyone! So excited to be here and learn from all your amazing expertise and experience. I’m a freelance copywriter in Madison, WI. I’ve made a huge career pivot after previously working as a birth doula and (most of) a graduate degree in clinical midwifery.
I came to copywriting in search of a creative, service-minded career that’s both remote work-friendly with a better work/life balance than birth work was. So far I’m loving it!

Working through the Comprehensive Copywriting Academy and Copyhackers’ Copy School right now while also doing some web copy work for small businesses primarily in the healthcare space. Would love to connect with other writers writing for healthcare!
